Usage (EN)

1 Install Ollama
   Follow the instructions on the Ollama website and make sure the ollama command works in your terminal.

2 Download the Mistral model

   bash
   ollama run mistral
   Wait until the model has been downloaded and started once; after that you can stop this command.

3 Start the PDA agent in the terminal

   bash
   cd /path/to/PDA_LLM
   python main.py

4 Chat
   After starting main.py you can talk directly with the PDA chatbot in the terminal.